      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click <uicontrol>Home</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>Enterprise Dashboard</uicontrol> is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol>Notifications</uicontrol>, and thenclick <uicontrol>My Tasks</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <note> The number of tasks pending on you is displayed adjacent to the <uicontrol>My Tasks</uicontrol> label in the navigation pane.</note>From the <uicontrol>MY TASKS</uicontrol> page, you can access records with a pending task. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content">For more information on completing a pending task, refer to <xref href="ComPendgTsk.xml"/>.</ph>
            </p>
